        <briefdescription>
<para>Calculates the spawn budget based on elapsed time. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Decrements the countdown by the frame&apos;s delta time. For each interval that has elapsed, increments the spawn budget by one. This handles frame spikes gracefully by spawning multiple objects if needed.</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>gameWorld</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Pointer to the current GameWorld. Unused. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>gameObjectPool</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Pointer to the pool. Unused. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>updateContext</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>The current frame&apos;s update context with delta time.</para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<simplesect kind="return"><para>The number of objects to spawn this frame based on elapsed intervals. </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
